# Financial Risk Credit Exposures Liquidity Or Underwriting Or Funding Facility Excluding Revolving With Early Amortisation Amount

## identifier
de12472

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of securitisation (including resecuritisation) exposures relating to liquidity, underwriting or funding facilities.  A liquidity, underwriting or funding facility will be considered an eligible facility when it meets the requirements as  detailed in the relevant prudential standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=FinancialRisk.Credit.ExposuresLiquidityOrUnderwritingOrFundingFacilityExcludingRevolvingWithEarlyAmortisation.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.09
- period=instant
